description: For more info: www.sweetwater.com On Sunday, March 20, 2011, legendary jazz bassist Stanley Clarke performed on both electric and acoustic bass at Sweetwater's Performance Theatre, sponsored by Ampeg bass amplifiers. Sweetwater Editorial Director Mitch Gallagher interviewed Mr. Clarke on a variety of topics before a capacity audience.
fulltitle: Sweetwater Minute - Vol. 83, Stanley Clarke Interview
